  "text": [
    "Someone enters: That alone",
    "makes me speak.",
    "When you lived, I spoke to you.",
    "We are transitive.",
    "I never dream of speech:",
    "I either speak or don\u2019t.",
    "And now that I know",
    "where you will not be\u2014",
    "I do not go there."
  ],
